 book is a comprehensive bibliography of Islamism in West Africa.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Jun 2022) 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / World / African.2bisacsh1 aCharlick, Robert B., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDarboe, Momodou N., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJourde, Cédric, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLe Vine, Victor, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLoimeier, Roman, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMiles, William F. S., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMiles, William F.S., eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aVillalón, Leonardo A., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertLynne Rienner Press Complete eBook-Package 2013-2000z978311078425140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978162637118740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781626371187423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781626371187/original  a978-3-11-078425-1  Lynne Rienner Press Complete eBook-Package 2013-2000c2000d2013  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_SN  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK